cs.DB, cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.PL 

This paper deals with verification of relational databases, which falls under the category of databases (cs.DB). The use of mu-calculus and the study of decidability suggest that this paper also belongs to the category of logic in computer science (cs.LO). The paper also deals with external services, which suggests that it may belong to the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) or distributed systems (cs.DS). Finally, the use of atomic actions and the manipulation of data suggest that this paper may also belong to the category of programming languages (cs.PL).
